{"tid":186544,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【IT人注意】邊個話做IT唔發達？ Google工程師人工高達9.4億","createTime":"2017-04-04T09:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T16:14:41.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"180e1a3c274a61bf098d7fd9b9d8b2d96dd5ae7f","tid":186544,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"香港做IT人一向被批評冇前途，「宅男先做」，香港創新科技局成立以來，沒突出建樹，不過各位IT人及工程師切勿灰心，因為Google一位開發無人駕駛技術的工程師，人工就高達9.4億（1.2億美元），恨死不少同行。<br />\n<br />\n事緣Google的無人駕駛子公司Waymo和Uber就一單無人駕駛技術官司正在審訊中，當中呈堂的人證及證物中，一位Google前工程師Anthony Levandowski的人工卻成為焦點，Anthony Levandowski為Google研究及開發無人駕駛技術時，所獲得的酬金高達1.2億美元，但其後Levandowski劈炮唔撈，自己成立研究無人駕駛的公司Otto，其後被Uber收購。<br />\n<br />\n案情指而Waymo控訴Levandowski從舊公司偷取大量無人駕駛技術的檔案及文件，要求法庭頒令，禁止Uber發展無人駕駛技術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjaHz63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjaHz63.jpg&h=9ae20590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56520054&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56520054%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170404&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a9ce44c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56520054%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170404&h=cfe10067\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56520054&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170404</a>"},{"pid":"bf9cfd0e1fcfbfd2bba615806110b579f597bba7","tid":186544,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:38:05.000Z","msg":"香港IT9咁得閒打J<br />\n<br />\n唔使換墨呀？"},{"pid":"c5d32ca63b4cc253747cd0f0f6226cb340838d60","tid":186544,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09: